zy></a></div><div class="col-custom-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-end"><div class="nav-top__footer-burger"><div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between w-100 h-100"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div></div></div><!----></div></div></nav><nav class="nav-bottom d-block d-lg-none"><div class="d-flex justify-content-around h-100 pt-2"><div class="nav-bottom__icon-wrapper text-center"><a class="d-block" href="/" aria-label="Strona główna" name="home-url"><svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-house nav-bottom__icons" style="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="house" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path class="" style="" fill="currentColor" d="M575.8 255.5c0 18-15 32.1-32 32.1l-32 0 .7 160.2c0 2.7-.2 5.4-.5 8.1l0 16.2c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40l-16 0c-1.1 0-2.2 0-3.3-.1c-1.4 .1-2.8 .1-4.2 .1L416 512l-24 0c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40l0-24 0-64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32l-64 0c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32l0 64 0 24c0 22.1-17.9 40-40 40l-24 0-31.9 0c-1.5 0-3-.1-4.5-.2c-1.2 .1-2.4 .2-3.6 .2l-16 0c-22.1 0-40-17.9-40-40l0-112c0-.9 0-1.9 .1-2.8l0-69.7-32 0c-18 0-32-14-32-32.1c0-9 3-17 10-24L266.4 8c7-7 15-8 22-8s15 2 21 7L564.8 231.5c8 7 12 15 11 24z"></path></svg></a><p class="nav-bottom__title"> Główna </p></div><div class="nav-bottom__icon-wrapper text-center"><a class="d-block" href="/najnowsze" name="newest-items" aria-label="Najnowsze"><svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-bell nav-bottom__icons" style="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="far" data-icon="bell" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path class="" style="" fill="currentColor" d="M224 0c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32l0 19.2C119 66 64 130.6 64 208l0 25.4c0 45.4-15.5 89.5-43.8 124.9L5.3 377c-5.8 7.2-6.9 17.1-2.9 25.4S14.8 416 24 416l400 0c9.2 0 17.6-5.3 21.6-13.6s2.9-18.2-2.9-25.4l-14.9-18.6C399.5 322.9 384 278.8 384 233.4l0-25.4c0-77.4-55-142-128-156.8L256 32c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32zm0 96c61.9 0 112 50.1 112 112l0 25