47e3-f485-4984-997a-76d2e6a9f1f1","2026-03-11 21:08:20","2a4a47e3-f485-4984-997a-76d2e6a9f1f1",{"id":1719,"name":83,"url":1720,"thumbnail":1720,"created_at":1721,"tags":83,"author":1396,"type":980,"filename":1722,"description":83,"750x750px":54,"160x90px":54,"365x225px":54,"100x100px":54,"760xautopx":54,"1200x675px":54,"gallery_id":1398},3785245,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/galleries/d50ee13f-973a-4453-bc6d-7ef1a0258fe8","2026-03-11 21:08:21","d50ee13f-973a-4453-bc6d-7ef1a0258fe8",{"id":1724,"name":83,"url":1725,"thumbnail":1725,"created_at":1721,"tags":83,"author":1396,"type":980,"filename":1726,"description":83,"750x750px":54,"160x90px":54,"365x225px":54,"100x100px":54,"760xautopx":54,"1200x675px":54,"gallery_id":1398},3785251,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/galleries/e6035487-f666-40b8-9f7a-e23ab329add7","e6035487-f666-40b8-9f7a-e23ab329add7",{"id":1728,"name":83,"url":1729,"thumbnail":1729,"created_at":1730,"tags":83,"author":1396,"type":980,"filename":1731,"description":83,"750x750px":54,"160x90px":54,"365x225px":54,"100x100px":54,"760xautopx":54,"1200x675px":54,"gallery_id":1398},3785257,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/galleries/9177b742-db97-4555-88a1-5620678e614d","2026-03-11 21:08:22","9177b742-db97-4555-88a1-5620678e614d","Y9YDsTgYFooExgQr2V5k",[1734,1735,1736,1737,1738,1739,1740,1741,1742,1743,1744,1745,1746,1240,1148,1747,1748],"derby","braci","fazekas","orlen","wisla","plock","wyszarpala","remis","z","pickiem","choc","mecz","dlugo","ukladal","zdjecia","Orlen Wisła Płock już od kilku tygodni była pewna trzeciego miejsca w grupie Ligi Mistrzów, a mimo to Nafciarze parli po zwycięstwo w Zagrzebiu. Wszystko wskazywało na to, że podopieczni Xaviego Sabate z Pickiem Szeged w meczu \"o nic\" dla mistrzów Polski też będą walczyć o zwycięstwo, ale czegoś zabrakło. Hiszpan szalał przy linii bocznej, wyraźnie niezadowolony z gry swojego zespołu, a jego zawodnicy przez całe 60 minut gonili wynik. W końcu udało im się na kilka minut przed końcem, a bramkę równo z syreną rzucił Melvyn Richardson.",{"title":1751,"description":1749,"keywords":1752,"fb_cover":1753,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Derby braci Fazekas. Orlen Wisła Płock wyszarpała remis z Pickiem, choć mecz długo się nie układał [ZDJĘCIA]","ORLEN Wisła Płock",{"value":1754},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-11 21:10:01","https://portalplock.pl/sport/derby-braci-fazekas-orlen-wisla-plock-wyszarpala-remis-z-pickiem-choc-mecz-dlugo-sie-nie-ukladal-zdjecia/Y9YDsTgYFooExgQr2V5k","derby-braci-fazekas-orlen-wisla-plock-wyszarpala-remis-z-pickiem-choc-mecz-dlugo-sie-nie-ukladal-zdjecia",[1752],[1760],{"tag":1752,"slug":1761},"orlen-wisla-plock",["Reactive",1763],{"ads":22,"aid":1764,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":1765,"author":979,"author_info":29,"category":1779,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":991,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":1780,"gallery_picked":23,"id":1781,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":1782,"lead":1791,"locked":29,"meta":1792,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_at":1797,"quiz_picked":54,"recommended":29,"redirect_url":54,"self_url":1798,"show_quiz_cover":23,"slug":1799,"sponsored":23,"short_title":1793,"tags":1800,"tagsRaw":1803,"title":1808,"type":1018,"uid":1781,"updated_at":1797},75214,[1766],{"id":1767,"name":83,"url":1768,"thumbnail":83,"created_at":1769,"tags":83,"author":1770,"type":980,"filename":1771,"description":1772,"750x750px":1773,"160x90px":1774,"365x225px":1775,"100x100px":1776,"760xautopx":1777,"1200x675px":1778,"article_id":1764},300226,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/bb9d1d30-12be-4313-b2ee-444e832fcaca","2026-03-11 20:51:16","Bartosz Miecznik","bb9d1d30-12be-4313-b2ee-444e832fcaca","KPS Płock wygrał fazę zasadniczą drugiej ligi","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/7e229ee3-609c-42b0-b64a-928c7796b113","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/cdccdd95-8e2d-44c2-b91e-32c443803328","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/b5beea6f-ba1e-44a1-bf67-cabde23b4b05","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/4d076db3-312e-4ae3-9a62-17a842dc1a00","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/4fcb53fc-97ca-439c-9651-45eddd974abd","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/b00d9880-8ff7-45ff-af9d-57d707e1c998",[137],{"id":54,"frequency":54},"rcBO8HLZa8CNkT1F6utl",[1783,1784,1739,1785,1332,1786,1787,1788,1332,1789,1790],"siatkarze","kps","ruszaja","walki","trudna","droga","pierwszej","ligi","KPS Płock na pierwszym miejscu zakończył fazę zasadniczą w grupie II drugiej ligi siatkarzy. Zespół, zyskujący coraz więcej kibiców, wygrał 19 meczów, a przegrał zaledwie trzy.",{"title":1793,"description":1791,"keywords":1794,"fb_cover":1795,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Siatkarze KPS Płock ruszają do walki. Trudna droga do pierwszej ligi","KPS Płock, siatkówka druga liga",{"value":1796},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-11 20:57:24","https://portalplock.pl/sport/siatkarze-kps-plock-ruszaja-do-walki-trudna-droga-do-pierwszej-ligi/rcBO8HLZa8CNkT1F6utl","siatkarze-kps-plock-ruszaja-do-walki-trudna-droga-do-pierwszej-ligi",[1801,1802],"KPS Płock","siatkówka druga liga",[1804,1806],{"tag":1801,"slug":1805},"kps-plock",{"tag":1802,"slug":1807},"siatkowka-druga-liga","Siatkarze KPS Płock ruszają do walki. Trudna droga do pierwszej ligi. Pomóżmy dopingiem!",["Reactive",1810],{"ads":22,"aid":1811,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":1812,"author":979,"author_info":29,"category":1825,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":991,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":1826,"gallery_picked":23,"id":1827,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":1828,"lead":1840,"locked":29,"meta":1841,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_at":1846,"quiz_picked":54,"recommended":29,"redirect_url":54,"self_url":1847,"show_quiz_cover":23,"slug":1848,"sponsored":23,"short_title":1849,"tags":1850,"tagsRaw":1851,"title":1854,"type":1018,"uid":1827,"updated_at":1846},75211,[1813],{"id":1814,"name":83,"url":1815,"thumbnail":83,"created_at":1816,"tags":83,"author":1817,"type":980,"filename":1818,"description":1274,"750x750px":1819,"160x90px":1820,"365x225px":1821,"100x100px":1822,"760xautopx":1823,"1200x675px":1824,"article_id":1811},300223,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/58f3605a-b665-4e29-96e4-210c2a5cbc56","2026-03-11 18:44:42","Mostostal Płock","58f3605a-b665-4e29-96e4-210c2a5cbc56","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/1bd76a18-ad20-496e-b937-8292764cce41","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/cca0bd54-401b-45cd-8525-af8622cd13a3","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/c6a9b8f4-5979-4340-97a2-dbaaf816c07f","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/b14573a7-5d6a-4a54-82f8-ec5dc79ad79e","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/ad976a57-d871-4178-accf-4662eecf25e7","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/295b16cc-2cab-4cb3-af66-140160e9f4da",[112],{"id":54,"frequency":54},"RKo2ONuAUNYyFqfMqOqH",[1829,1830,1831,1742,1832,1833,1834,1835,1836,1837,1838,1839],"potezne","pieniadze","firma","plocka","ma","kontrakt","na","ponad","122","mln","zl","Zarząd Mostostalu Płock poinformował w środę 11 marca, że spółka ta podpisała z Orlenem aneks do umowy na wykonanie zbiornika o pojemności 50.000 m3 do magazynowania ropy naftowej.",{"title":1842,"description":1840,"keywords":1843,"fb_cover":1844,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Potężne pieniądze. Firma z Płocka ma kontrakt na ponad 122 mln zł","mostostal płock",{"value":1845},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-11 18:46:38","https://portalplock.pl/wiadomosci/potezne-pieniadze-firma-z-plocka-ma-kontrakt-na-ponad-122-mln-zl/RKo2ONuAUNYyFqfMqOqH","potezne-pieniadze-firma-z-plocka-ma-kontrakt-na-ponad-122-mln-zl","Firma z Płocka z kontraktem na ponad 122 mln zł",[1843],[1852],{"tag":1843,"slug":1853},"mostostal-plock","Potężne pieniądze. Firma z Płocka z kontraktem na ponad 122 mln zł",["Reactive",1856],{"ads":22,"aid":1857,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":1858,"author":1041,"author_info":37,"category":1871,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":1044,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":1872,"gallery_picked":23,"id":1873,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":1874,"lead":1887,"locked":29,"meta":1888,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_at":1893,"quiz_picked":54,"recommended":29,"redirect_url":54,"self_url":1894,"show_quiz_cover":23,"slug":1895,"sponsored":23,"short_title":1896,"tags":1897,"tagsRaw":1900,"title":1889,"type":1018,"uid":1873,"updated_at":1893},75202,[1859],{"id":1860,"name":83,"url":1861,"thumbnail":83,"created_at":1862,"tags":83,"author":1863,"type":980,"filename":1864,"description":83,"750x750px":1865,"160x90px":1866,"365x225px":1867,"100x100px":1868,"760xautopx":1869,"1200x675px":1870,"article_id":1857},300217,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/86864cb1-2524-4ff3-96e7-eb09fcf78fd1","2026-03-11 15:16:01","FB: Saszan","86864cb1-2524-4ff3-96e7-eb09fcf78fd1","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/9ed746a8-783c-4669-ae3e-f57d1c3d605b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/e41d9950-582c-425f-85ef-6bf0080190fa","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/05867195-ffbc-4b19-93b0-2df940fb1edc","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/828ba7e5-61c9-4338-9814-a405881e2193","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/b3bbb132-6605-472b-a7d8-6efc4956f32d","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/38a4de8f-489d-4497-81ea-cbaa19877197",[112],{"id":54,"frequency":54},"JEmJMbupVdzgC5w5x8B1",[1875,1288,1876,1051,1055,1877,1878,1879,1880,1881,1882,1883,1884,1885,1886],"piosenkarka","wystapic","to","byloby","niesamowite","wydarzenie","dla","calej","szkoly","podala","jeden","warunek","W mediach społecznościowych coraz większą popularność zdobywa trend, na którym - głównie młode osoby - proszą artystów, celebrytów lub polityków czy zrobią coś dla nich. Ci wyrażają zgodę pod warunkiem, że uda im się zebrać określoną liczbę polubień na Facebooku bądź TikToku. W ten sposób m.in. uczniowie z Wolanowa wywalczyli wspólnego kebaba z prezydentem Karolem Nawrockim. Teraz o koncert znanej piosenkarki w płockiej szkole stara się jedna z uczennic.",{"title":1889,"description":1887,"keywords":1890,"fb_cover":1891,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Piosenkarka może wystąpić w Płocku. \"To byłoby niesamowite wydarzenie dla całej szkoły\". Podała jeden warunek","koncert, Szkoła Podstawowa Płock",{"value":1892},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-11 15:17:27","https://portalplock.pl/wiadomosci/piosenkarka-moze-wystapic-w-plocku-to-byloby-niesamowite-wydarzenie-dla-calej-szkoly-podala-jeden-warunek/JEmJMbupVdzgC5w5x8B1","piosenkarka-moze-wystapic-w-plocku-to-byloby-niesamowite-wydarzenie-dla-calej-szkoly-podala-jeden-warunek","Piosenkarka może wystąpić w Płocku. Podała jeden warunek",[1898,1899],"koncert","Szkoła Podstawowa Płock",[1901,1902],{"tag":1898,"slug":1898},{"tag":1899,"slug":1903},"szkola-podstawowa-plock",["Reactive",1905],{"ads":22,"aid":1906,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":1907,"author":1041,"author_info":37,"category":1920,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":1044,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":1921,"gallery_picked":23,"id":1922,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":1923,"lead":1929,"locked":29,"meta":1930,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_at":1935,"quiz_picked":54,"recommended":29,"redirect_url":54,"self_url":1936,"show_quiz_cover":23,"slug":1937,"sponsored":23,"short_title":1931,"tags":1938,"tagsRaw":1941,"title":1931,"type":1018,"uid":1922,"updated_at":1935},75205,[1908],{"id":1909,"name":83,"url":1910,"thumbnail":83,"created_at":1911,"tags":83,"author":1912,"type":980,"filename":1913,"description":83,"750x750px":1914,"160x90px":1915,"365x225px":1916,"100x100px":1917,"760xautopx":1918,"1200x675px":1919,"article_id":1906},300214,"https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/23ac324c-1d1a-45c6-864a-e6906d95a60b","2026-03-11 15:02:22","KMP Płock","23ac324c-1d1a-45c6-864a-e6906d95a60b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/a8dea3fe-a838-4572-a9e6-fa6777fb7a8c","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/adb87200-7524-48ef-9b83-8d34412a748a","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/b20ba618-e03a-4ad6-9ffc-b78d80d1030b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/ffc4ff68-ad1f-46ad-94b2-f44743277a52","https: