0071d02-7e7d-4e62-933a-b1f68c846dd5","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/db43cb4d-b39e-4821-bcbd-bff09c474d0b","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/c65a9947-7b79-47fc-9d05-8d5375afd7ee","https://storage.googleapis.com/patrykslezak-pbem/plock/articles/image/f25d216a-7361-4731-9396-cc72cfdaafda",[112],{"id":54,"frequency":54},"NK49khdVE17diAUp9QCV",[2231,2232,2233,1241,2234,2235,1835,2236,1287,1877,1148,2237,2238,2239],"ona","pijana","on","bardziej","prowadzili","zmiane","koniec","tej","przygody","To nie była typowa interwencja płockich policjantów. Zatrzymali oni samochód osobowy, któego pasażerowie, na widok mundurowych, zamienili się miejscami. Okazało się, że zarówno mężczyzna, jak i kobieta byli nietrzeźwi, a to dopiero początek ich problemów.",{"title":2242,"description":2240,"keywords":2243,"fb_cover":2244,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Ona pijana, on jeszcze bardziej. Prowadzili \"na zmianę\", a to nie koniec tej \"przygody\"","Policja Płock",{"value":2245},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-10 18:58:04","https://portalplock.pl/wiadomosci/ona-pijana-on-jeszcze-bardziej-prowadzili-na-zmiane-a-to-nie-koniec-tej-przygody/NK49khdVE17diAUp9QCV","ona-pijana-on-jeszcze-bardziej-prowadzili-na-zmiane-a-to-nie-koniec-tej-przygody",[1940],[2251],{"tag":1940,"slug":1944},["Reactive",2253],{"ads":22,"aid":2254,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":2255,"author":2268,"author_info":29,"category":2269,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":2270,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":2271,"gallery_picked":23,"id":2272,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":2273,"lead":2280,"locked":29,"meta":2281,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_a