","pkp","powazny","problem","szczegolnie","sytuacjach","naglych","- PKP nie realizuje wyroku sądu. Przejazd kolejowy nadal zablokowany - grzmi w swoich mediach społecznościowych Urząd Gminy Nowy Duninów. Blokada ma sprawiać problemy nie tylko mieszkańcom, ale również służbom ratunkowym. W sprawie wystosowano nawet interpelację do ministra sprawiedliwości.",{"title":2406,"description":2404,"keywords":83,"fb_cover":2407,"fb_title":54,"fb_description":54},"Gmina kontra PKP. \"To poważny problem – szczególnie w sytuacjach nagłych\"",{"value":2408},{"filename":54,"name":54,"tags":54,"thumbnail":54,"type":54,"url":54},"2026-03-10 16:27:07","https://portalplock.pl/wiadomosci/gmina-kontra-pkp-to-powazny-problem-szczegolnie-w-sytuacjach-naglych/OryjX21J3DJhY3vHReXR","gmina-kontra-pkp-to-powazny-problem-szczegolnie-w-sytuacjach-naglych","Gmina i Nadleśnictwo kontra PKP. \"Spółka nie realizuje wyroku sądu\"",[2414,2415],"PKP","Nowy Duninów",[2417,2418],{"tag":2414,"slug":2398},{"tag":2415,"slug":2419},"nowy-duninow","Gmina i Nadleśnictwo kontra PKP. \"Spółka nie realizuje wyroku sądu. To poważny problem – szczególnie w sytuacjach nagłych\"",["Reactive",2422],{"ads":22,"aid":2423,"alternative_gallery_style":22,"attachments":2424,"author":1097,"author_info":37,"category":2436,"comments":22,"comments_auth":22,"content":83,"created_by":1100,"created_by_name":83,"custom_html":54,"featured":29,"gallery_ads":2437,"gallery_picked":23,"id":2438,"is_advertisement":29,"is_photostory":29,"is_pool":29,"multiportal":54,"view_type":54,"is_redirect":29,"keywords":2439,"lead":2451,"locked":29,"meta":2452,"parent_domain":54,"parent_id":54,"photostory_added":23,"pool_picked":54,"pool_under_photostory":23,"premium":29,"published":37,"published_at":2457,"quiz_picked":54,"recommended":29,"redirect_url":54,"self_url":2458,"show_quiz_cover":23,"slug":2459,"sponsored":23,"short_title":2453,"tags":2460,"tagsRaw":2461,"title":2453,"type":1018,"uid":2438,"updated_at":2464},75172,[2425],{"id":2426,"name":